OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright spells first thing,
OL,6,Fbut a cloudy start for many. Bright or
OL,7,Fsunny conditions developing through
OL,8,Fthe day for most, but remaining cloudy
OL,9,Facross Kent with coastal showers
OL,10,Fpushing inland. Feeling cooler along
OL,11,Feastern coasts in northeasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers across Kent continue
OL,14,Finto the night, easing off into the
OL,15,Fearly hours. Elsewhere a cold, and
OL,16,Fperhaps frosty, night in places seeing
OL,17,Fpersistent clear skies, mainly in the
OL,18,Fnorthwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
