OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FVariable cloud for much of
OL,6,Fthe day but staying dry, with
OL,7,Foccasional bright or sunny intervals
OL,8,Fand temperatures higher than
OL,9,FWednesday. Cooler for coastal areas in
OL,10,Fbreezier conditions.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,13,Fbrings sunny spells and scattered
OL,14,Fshowers. Rain or showers, occasionally
OL,15,Fheavy, are likely on Saturday at some
OL,16,Fpoint. Sunday appears drier away from
OL,17,Fsouthern coasts, where heavy showers
OL,18,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
